@startuml
title Workflow Execution Sequence

actor User
participant "Frontend UI" as UI
participant "API Service" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Redis Queue" as Queue
participant "Worker Service" as Worker
participant "Runtime Environment" as Runtime

User -> UI: Create/Trigger Workflow
UI -> API: POST /api/v1/workflows/{id}/run
API -> DB: Validate workflow exists
DB -> API: Return workflow definition
API -> Queue: Queue workflow execution task
Queue -> Worker: Task available notification
Worker -> Queue: Claim task
Worker -> API: Fetch workflow definition
API -> Worker: Return workflow definition
Worker -> Runtime: Execute workflow nodes
Runtime -> Worker: Return execution results
Worker -> DB: Update execution status
Worker -> API: Notify completion
API -> UI: Return execution status
UI -> User: Display results

@enduml